297
00:23:38,039 --> 00:23:38,790
Andem!

298
00:23:43,419 --> 00:23:45,546
<i>Little Geek está no caso.</i>

299
00:23:55,556 --> 00:23:59,310
<i>Aqui fala o Monk, Senhor.
