359
00:30:50,138 --> 00:30:52,765
Espera aí, Jammer. Segure-se nisso aí...

360
00:31:00,022 --> 00:31:00,857
Merda!

361
00:31:02,483 --> 00:31:04,444
Bud? Está me ouvindo?

362
00:31:05,278 --> 00:31:05,987
Bud?

363
00:31:11,159 --> 00:31:12,201
Diabo!

364
00:31:24,881 --> 00:31:26,007
Oh, meu Deus!

365
00:31:56,829 --> 00:31:57,914
Bud, é você?

366
00:32:21,187 --> 00:32:22,647
